document.full_text: in a renewed attack against president barack obama's healthcare overhaul program, house republicans voted on tuesday to deny funding for a central element of the law that sets up marketplaces for people to shop for health insurance coverage.
document.title: u.s. republicans push to repeal healthcare funds
lines_and_colors: in a renewed attack against president barack obama's healthcare overhaul program, house republicans voted on tuesday to deny funding for a central element of the law that sets up marketplaces for people to shop for health insurance coverage.
